<abstract label="Abstract" encodinganalog="545">The Columbian Literary Society was founded in 1846.  The Hesperian Literary Society was founded in 1851.</abstract>


<abstract encodinganalog="520">Records of both the Columbian Literary Society and Hesperian Literary Society documenting their activities.  Included are numerous minute books, roll books, treasurer's books, book lists, constitutions and bylaws as well as some correspondence and programs for events co-hosted by the societies.</abstract>

</did>

